        <h3>Future Visits</h3>
        <p>Based on your goals and the doctor’s recommendations, you will likely have a follow up visit that will consist primarily of treatment. This will range in number depending on the condition and extent of injury. Each follow up visit can take 10-30 minutes and we will let you know ahead of time how much time you will need to plan for.</p>        
